lyrics:
[verse]
Oh Ilayda, the morning sun shines upon you
Every day, you bring joy anew
With a smile brighter than the day
Günaydın Ilayda, I just have to say

[chorus]
You light up every room, can't you see
Günaydın Ilayda, you're a melody
Your laughter is contagious, it sets me free
Günaydın Ilayda, you're the sweetest melody
